title: Liberty's Samantha Peterson, Madelyn Conrad are lehighvalleylive Girls Tennis Players of the Week
text:
Samantha Peterson and Madelyn Conrad , Liberty 
The Liberty seniors posted a 6-0, 6-1 win over Freedom's Natalie Sinai and Kaitlyn Swint to win the District 11 Class AAA doubles title on Monday at Lehigh University. 
Peterson and Conrad, the silver medalists from last year, didn't lose a set the entire tournament and only fell in 11 games in five matches. 
Conrad won No. 2 singles and Peterson finished third at No. 1 singles at the Eastern Pennsylvania Conference tournament last Saturday. 
HONORABLE MENTION: Fr. Elessa Jacobs , Easton; Jr. Brooke Adams , Bethlehem Catholic; Fr. Halle DeNardo , Nazareth; Jr. Madison Stewart , Nazareth; Sr. Tori Evert , Bethlehem Catholic; Jr. Gabby Duffy , Bethlehem Catholic; Jr. Allie Palmisano , Bethlehem Catholic; Sr. Bailee Deshler , Bethlehem Catholic.
